Like everyone else, you also want to try out a latest car racing challenge every day. However, what will happen when you get a chance to play something different related to car games. Luckily, we have got you covered today with a brand new racing game where you have to perform different tasks including fuel refilling, driving cars, as well as washing and parking on the given location. Are you able enough to take care of three jobs in a single game? Join Car Wash & Gas Station Simulator and gear up to witness the best car fun you have ever witnessed online!

This cool HTML5 online game allows you to enjoy a matchless driving and parking experience. There are plenty of challenging and addictive missions and levels to play through. During the gameplay, make sure to keep your eyes on the fuel gauge. If you are ready to drive your car to the washing centre, make sure to refill the fuel gauge. Once washing is done, get ready to reach out to the finish line by following the arrow.

Start the engine and gear up to drive and park-like never before in this one of the best car driving simulator games for boys! Do not forget to turn off the engine when the fuel is filling. Be careful and try to be as fast as you can to complete your mission before it is too late! Pay money before washing your car! Now follow the instructions to wash and make it clean and look like a new one! Good luck trying more addictive car games online and have fun with your friends without download!
